} Initiate the Model import job (in the Model Hosting account)In this step, we execute the model import job using the AWS Command Line Interface (AWS CLI) command. You can also use AWS SDKs or APIs for the same purpose. Run the following command from your terminal session with an IAM user or role that has the necessary privileges to create a custom model import job. You don’t need to explicitly provide an ARN or details of the CMK used by the Model Development team.aws bedrock create-model-import-job \
